            <div class="imagegroup">
                <img src="images/4_m1_f4-no.jpg" alt="Figure 4 – Age-adjusted lifetime risk of MS, showing risk for first-degree relatives, second-degree 
                    relatives and the general population"
                    class="zoomable" />
